reviewText: This video is disappointing only because there is absolutely no narration explaining what one is seeing although the wonderful music by Norwegian composers certainly makes for a perfect blend of music and scenery.  The inclusion of the World Heritage site of Roros would also have been nice.
This is the worst journey ever . There is no harmoney whatsoever between music and scenery . Some scenes are repeated more than enough , others are stupid. My advice is DO NOT BUY IT.
